The paper discusses a privacy standard for collecting and analyzing data, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes novel mechanisms for collecting multidimensional data, which involves data management (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the accuracy of the proposed mechanisms, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT).
